text: Enicodes schreibersii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1865. It is known from New Caledonia. It feeds on the breadfruit tree.BioLib.cz - Enicodes schreibersii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1865
